---
title: Southern-Spiced Beef Tostadas with Yoghurt & Cheddar
description: Gather the troops for a Southern-style tostada fiesta! Place the toppings in the centre of the table and let everyone create their
own – with mildly spiced beef chilli, Cheddar cheese, tomato and yoghurt, they'll be spoiled for choice!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-beef-tostadas-14617888.jpg
